{"title":"2020-06-13","virtualPath":"/Diary/","html":"<p>生きてたのか、あいつ。。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>買い物帰りの金沢駅前。ラティ数匹ぐらいいるかと思ったらまったくいない。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-193059-P_20200613_193059_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-193059-P_20200613_193059_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"駅1\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-204617-P_20200613_204617_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-204617-P_20200613_204617_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"駅2\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>いない。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-193357-Screenshot_20200613-193357.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-193357-Screenshot_20200613-193357.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"ジム\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>雨で予定が狂ったので宝達山で体ほぐし。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-134859-P_20200613_134859_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-134859-P_20200613_134859_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"ゆり？1\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-134905-P_20200613_134905_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-134905-P_20200613_134905_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"ゆり？2\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>salomon のシューズは文句のつけようがない。雨でもしっかりグリップする。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-140226-P_20200613_140226_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-140226-P_20200613_140226_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"シューズ\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>山頂はガスガス。人もほとんどいない。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-140615-P_20200613_140615_vHDR_Auto_HP.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-140615-P_20200613_140615_vHDR_Auto_HP.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"山頂1\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-141237-P_20200613_141237_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-141237-P_20200613_141237_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"山頂2\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>ここも金になった。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-122756-Screenshot_20200613-122756.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-122756-Screenshot_20200613-122756.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>これで白山山域は知ってる限り、全部金かな。スプーに邪魔されながら、よくがんばった。おれ。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>本日の最大強化。意外と強いのねー</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-080440-Screenshot_20200613-080440.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-06-13/20200613-080440-Screenshot_20200613-080440.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"グレイシア\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記","updated":"2020-06-17T03:24:50","published":"2020-06-17T03:24:50"}